description: Lawrence Cutajar had been criticised over the inquiry into journalist Daphne Caruana Galizia's death.
title: Daphne Caruana Galizia case: Under-fire Malta police chief quits
title_page: Daphne Caruana Galizia case: Under-fire Malta police chief quits - BBC News
maintext: Mr Abela said he found no reason to dismiss Mr Grech. But he said a new, "transparent" method for appointing the Maltese police commissioner would be examined. Currently it is the PM's choice, not parliament's.
